ata/daily_data_e.html?hlyRange=%7C&dlyRange=1921-04-01%7C1976-01-31&mlyRange=1921-01-01%7C1976-12-01&StationID=4112&Prov=ON&urlExtension=_e.html&searchType=stnProx&optLimit=specDate&Month=12&Day=1&StartYear=1840&EndYear=2016&Year=1933&selRowPerPage=25&Line=1&txtRadius=25&optProxType=navLink&txtLatDecDeg=46.483333333333&txtLongDecDeg=80.983333333333&timeframe=2\n| title = December 1933\n| work = Canadian Climate Data\n| accessdate = June 17, 2016}}</ref><ref name= EnvironmentCanada>{{cite web\n| publisher = [[Environment Canada]]\n| url = http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climate_normals/results_1981_2010_e.html?stnID=4132&lang=e&dCode=1&province=ONT&provBut=Go&month1=0&month2=12\n| title = Sudbury A, Ontario\n| work = Canadian Climate Normals 1981\u20132010\n| accessdate = April 12, 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"November 1887\">{{cite web\n| publisher = [[Environment Canada]]\n| url = http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climate_data/daily_data_e.html?hlyRange=%7C&dlyRange=1887-06-01%7C1977-09-30&mlyRange=1914-01-01%7C1977-12-01&StationID=4131&Prov=ON&urlExtension=_e.html&searchType=stnProx&optLimit=specDate&StartYear=1840&EndYear=2016&selRowPerPage=25&Line=0&txtRadius=25&optProxType=navLink&txtLatDecDeg=46.466666666667&txtLongDecDeg=80.816666666667&timeframe=2&Year=1887&Month=11\n| title = November 1887\n| work = Canadian Climate Data\n| accessdate = June 17, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"January 1888\">{{cite web\n| publisher = [[Environment Canada]]\n| url = http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climate_data/daily_data_e.html?hlyRange=%7C&dlyRange=1887-06-01%7C1977-09-30&mlyRange=1914-01-01%7C1977-12-01&StationID=4131&Prov=ON&urlExtension=_e.html&searchType=stnProx&optLimit=specDate&StartYear=1840&EndYear=2016&selRowPerPage=25&Line=0&txtRadius=25&optProxType=navLink&txtLatDecDeg=46.466666666667&txtLongDecDeg=80.816666666667&timeframe=2&Year=1888&Month=1\n| title = January 1888\n| work = Canadian Climate Data\n| accessdate = June 17, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"February 1888\">{{cite web\n| publisher 