ences==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Merrillan, Wisconsin}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170911191026/http://achm.k12.wi.us/ Alma Center-Humbird-Merrilan School District]\n* Sanborn fire insurance maps: [http://content.wisconsinhistory.org/cdm/ref/collection/maps/id/8019 1904] [http://content.wisconsinhistory.org/cdm/ref/collection/maps/id/8021 1914]\n\n{{Jackson County, Wisconsin}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Jackson County, Wisconsin]]\n[[Category:Villages in Wisconsin]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name            = Merrillan, Wisconsin\n|settlement_type          = [[Village (United States)|Village]]\n|nickname                 = \n|motto                    = \n\n<!-- Images -->\n|image_skyline            = Merrillan.jpg\n|imagesize                = 250px\n|image_caption            = Downtown Merrillan\n|image_flag               = \n|image_seal               = \n\n<!-- Maps -->\n|image_map                = File:Jackson County Wisconsin Incorporated and Unincorporated areas Merrillan Highlighted.svg\n|mapsize                  = 250px\n|map_caption              = Location of Merrillan in Jackson County, Wisconsin.\n|image_map1               = \n|mapsize1                 = \n|map_caption1             = \n\n<!-- Location -->\n|subdivision_type         = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_name         = {{flag|United States}}\n|subdivision_type1        = [[U.S. state|State]]\n|subdivision_name1        = {{flag|Wisconsin}}\n|subdivision_type2        = [[List of counties in Wisconsin|County]]\n|subdivision_name2        = [[Jackson County, Wisconsin|Jackson]]\n\n<!-- Government -->\n|government_footnotes     = \n|government_type          = \n|leader_title             = \n|leader_name              = \n|leader_title1            = \n|leader_name1             = \n|established_title        = \n|established_date         = \n\n<!-- Area -->\n|unit_pref                = Imperial\n|area_footn